    <h2>
      <a href="/episodes/63-model-name-in-url-revised">Model Name in URL (revised)</a>
      
    </h2>
    <div class="description">
      A model&#x27;s ID in the URL is not very helpful to the user. Consider adding the name which can also improve SEO. Learn how to override to_param, add a slug attribute, and make a catch all route for deep nesting.
      <span class="stats">(9 minutes)</span>
